      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, just a quick question about my meds. I've been on 5mg of warfarin for a while now for my heart stuff but honestly I feel totally fine lately, no issues at all. I was thinking of maybe dropping down to 2mg just to keep it more natural if I'm doing well? seems like a lot to be taking if I'm feeling healthy.",
